OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FCentral Belt
OL,6,Fand the south mainly dry with just a
OL,7,Flittle patchy rain, although some
OL,8,Fpersistent rain likely later in the
OL,9,Fnight. Occasional rain turning more
OL,10,Fpersistent across Argyll. Mild.
OL,11,
OL,12,CWednesday:FCloudy and mild with
OL,13,Foutbreaks of rain, this most
OL,14,Fpersistent and occasionally heavy
OL,15,Facross Argyll.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
