OL,5,COutlook for Thursday to Saturday:
OL,6,FUnsettled with showers or longer
OL,7,Fspells of rain on Thursday. Chance of
OL,8,Frain at first on Friday, otherwise
OL,9,Fbright with a few showers. Rain
OL,10,Fspreading east on Saturday.
